pullRequest.body:
~~We may migrate to `Quot` and `IsEquiv` APIs in the future, but it might be a good start to clean up `Quotient` APIs anyway.~~

The diffs in this PR did not include `QuotLike` APIs, but eventually I decided to migrate to `QuotLike` before deprecating some old APIs. This is because some lemmas don't have alternatives that don't use `¬∑ ‚âà ¬∑`, and the alternatives that use `¬∑ ‚âà ¬∑` are in the core. See [Zulip](https://leanprover.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/113488-general/topic/.60.28.C2.B7.20.E2.89.88.20.C2.B7.29.60.20in.20.60Quotient.60.20APIs/near/466970386).
